com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.core.classabstraction
Class KeYJavaMethod

java.lang.Object
  com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.core.classabstraction.KeYJavaMethod

public class KeYJavaMethod
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates information regarding a single Java method. The information contained in an instance of this class is sufficient to facilitate symbolic execution of the method.

Author:
christopher
